              <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">The operator already uses Salesforce → <strong class="text-slate-100">use Salesforce</strong>. The data migration cost of switching CRMs exceeds any agent-friendliness benefit. Work with the admin to get a connected app configured.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-400 font-mono text-sm shrink-0 mt-0.5">IF</span>
