            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-amber-400 font-mono text-sm shrink-0 mt-0.5">ALWAYS</span>
              <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">Call the Describe endpoint before any CRUD operation to discover the org's custom fields and validation rules. Hardcoded field lists will break across different customer orgs.</p>
            </div>
