              <span class="text-red-400 font-mono text-sm shrink-0 mt-0.5">NEVER</span>
              <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">Assume sandbox behavior matches production. Verify connected app configuration, field availability, and governor limits separately in each environment.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
